{"tid":2049371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博社：香港電訊或出售PCCW Global 估值10億美元","createTime":"2020-06-03T11:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T04:04:13.000Z","uid":21470,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb90088aaf0c59ec9ac68724a93fe0bad8f47df","tid":2049371,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"傳香港電訊或出售PCCW Global<br />\n2020-06-03 HKT 19:48<br />\n<br />\n彭博社引述知情人士指，香港電訊正考慮出售國際企業業務PCCW Global，估值或高達10億美元，預計可能吸引其他電訊公司或私募基金接手。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，出售仍處於初期考慮階段，正式程序或在今年較後時間啟動，香港電訊未就交易結構作決定，亦有機會不出售相關資產。<br />\n<br />\n香港電訊回應本台查詢表示，不評論市場傳聞，但強調PCCW Global是香港電訊業務重要一環。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530005-20200603.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530005-20200603.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=7596e8d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530005-20200603.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5a1bb995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530005-20200603.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"35c3f3d0284da1f9639b9435b165da9188865dd2","tid":2049371,"uid":73856,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:00:49.000Z","msg":"走呀走呀"},{"pid":"368feb37742568557212a3bfb536cd97bafbffa1","tid":2049371,"uid":25468,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"肯定又係中資接貨"},{"pid":"0ec8826eb9263554dfe21c4b37a690f131376780","tid":2049371,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"368feb37742568557212a3bfb536cd97bafbffa1","tid":2049371,"uid":25468,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"肯定又係中資接貨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:13:22.000Z","msg":"我都覺得咁唔係一件好事"},{"pid":"25a720cf1fea526693480073cb831ca